George Magnus , senior economic 
adviser at  UBS Investment Bank , says the European debt crisis 
"is going to deteriorate" unless policymakers can change their 
"single minded focus" on austerity.  Magnus talks with 
Bloomberg's Ken Prewitt and  Tom Keene  on Bloomberg Radio's 
"Bloomberg Surveillance."     (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 12:34
 